{
  "title": "Simple ClickHouse (Prometheus, без OTel)",
  "uid": "ch-simple-prometheus",
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "time": { "from": "now-24h", "to": "now" },
  "timezone": "browser",
  "tags": ["clickhouse", "prometheus", "siem"],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "ℹ️ О дашборде ClickHouse (Prometheus)",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 3 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## ClickHouse через Prometheus (без OTel)\n\n**Почему линии «скучные»:** память и свободный диск меняются медленно; **rate(Query)** и **InsertedRows** живее. Если в списке ещё есть старый **Simple ClickHouse OTel** с пустыми OTel-панелями — это другой дашборд; используйте этот (**uid** `ch-simple-prometheus`).\n\n**SIEM-события** — дашборд **SIEM-Lite Overview** (ClickHouse SQL).\n\n**Настройка:** `deploy/docker/clickhouse/config.d/prometheus.xml`"
      },
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "CPU (прокси: SelectQuery / с)",
      "description": "В ТЗ: rate(ClickHouseProfileEvents_SelectQuery[2m]) как индикатор нагрузки CPU/запросов.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 3, "w": 12, "h": 7 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-siem" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "rate(ClickHouseProfileEvents_SelectQuery{job=\"clickhouse\"}[2m])", "legendFormat": "SelectQuery/s" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "cps", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 18 } } },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }, "legend": { "displayMode": "hidden" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Memory (ClickHouseMetrics_MemoryTracking)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 3, "w": 12, "h": 7 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-siem" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "ClickHouseMetrics_MemoryTracking{job=\"clickhouse\"}", "legendFormat": "MemoryTracking" },
        { "refId": "B", "expr": "ClickHouseAsyncMetrics_MemoryResident{job=\"clickhouse\"}", "legendFormat": "MemoryResident (async)" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "bytes", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2 } } },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }, "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Disk available (default)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 10, "w": 12, "h": 7 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-siem" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "ClickHouseAsyncMetrics_DiskAvailable_default{job=\"clickhouse\"}", "legendFormat": "available" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "bytes", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2 } } },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }, "legend": { "displayMode": "hidden" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Queries / с (ClickHouseProfileEvents_Query)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 10, "w": 12, "h": 7 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-siem" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "rate(ClickHouseProfileEvents_Query{job=\"clickhouse\"}[2m])", "legendFormat": "Query/s" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "cps", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2 } } },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }, "legend": { "displayMode": "hidden" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Вставленные строки / с",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 17, "w": 24, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-siem" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "rate(ClickHouseProfileEvents_InsertedRows{job=\"clickhouse\"}[2m])", "legendFormat": "inserted rows/s" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "cps", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 15 } } },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }, "legend": { "displayMode": "hidden" } }
    }
  ]
}
